      "description": "Honest little car looking for its next owner. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s an affordable option for someone who wants basic wheels, a project, or a handy runabout. Great chance to get into a car without spending a fortune, and with a bit of care it could still be a really useful ride. Priced to sell and open to sensible interest.",
